{"tid":2326784,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"三名速龍隊員 對肺炎測試呈陽性反應。","createTime":"2020-12-15T14:26:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-15T15:26:22.000Z","uid":53705,"like":43,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"462fe596cc19b2301781be065170d9cb72aac719","tid":2326784,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T14:26:48.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports】速龍周一宣佈，在訓練營之前的NBA強制測試中，有3名速龍成員對新冠肺炎測試呈陽性反應。<br />\n<br />\n速龍在一份聲明中說，「這3名成員將繼續自我隔離。到目前為止，測試後續和緊密接觸追蹤都顯示，沒有其他速龍成員受感染。我們將繼續遵守安全協議，並將更新情況。」 出於私隱的考慮，速龍方面沒有說明誰的測試結果是陽性，也沒有說明他們是球員還是團隊成員。球隊亦拒絕透露這3名成員有否出現新冠肺炎的任何症狀、進行特定測試的日期和團隊何時獲得這些結果。 速龍總經理韋伯斯特（Bobby Webster）說，「我們都習慣於早上起床，下樓，接受檢查，戴著口罩，拿了食物在房間吃東西，直接上巴士，與社會保持距離。練習時大家在一起的時候，球員們沒有戴口罩。我認為這對我們來說已經變得非常正常和已是常規了。」"},{"pid":"77cd3f3d1a75293a0bcd5e33c7d30e50e7c184f3","tid":2326784,"uid":79793,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T14:28:54.000Z","msg":"Check埋老婆安全啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可能係我傳染"},{"pid":"33b2cf8b3ee325860f223c1903238d88b8ee6a95","tid":2326784,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T14:29:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"590fbe7d55c6cc46ccce5597e461f6124f3b3d5b","tid":2326784,"uid":79117,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T14:29:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b284b6c077a0e2a5d1f3d707d18e898b530f18ae","tid":2326784,"uid":132572,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T14:30:02.000Z","msg":"屌你NBA"},{"pid":"952a4eef8803e3d6f50ee1e9a3d6